title: Dead Air (Slave Labor-1989)(Rumor-Novus-HD-Year Two) Mike Allred
description:
The world has ended, and Calvin Lennox just wants to find his way back to his wife and two sons. When he and three friends escape from their 'safe' small town, he finds that the end of the world isn't quite what he was expecting.


Very early work of renowned comic book artist Michael D. Allred, whose works include Golden Plates, Madman and X-Force. This is a complete graphic novel and shows the skill that made Allred a fan favorite.
